      </div>
      <h1 class="font-display text-h1 text-white mb-6 drop-shadow-lg max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        Developing Capable, Confident, Curious Children
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/90 font-corp-body max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Our mission is to transform how children learn by focusing on real skill development through engaging, badge-based education that prepares them for life‚Äînot just tests.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Problem We're Solving -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-h2 text-text-dark mb-6">The Problem With Traditional Education</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-text-body font-corp-body">
            <p>
              For decades, education has focused on grades, test scores, and seat time. Students memorize facts to pass exams, then quickly forget what they "learned."
            </p>
            <p>
              This system produces students who can ace tests but struggle with real-world challenges. They've collected credentials without developing genuine capabilities.
            </p>
            <p>
              Meanwhile, children lose their natural love of learning, viewing education as something to endure rather than enjoy.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-red-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border-2 border-red-200">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="text-3xl">üìä</span>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-display text-text-dark mb-1">Grades Over Growth</h4>
